VAIFORM — DOCS RULES

Applies to:
- docs/**
- ROUTE_TRUTH_TABLE.md
- VAIFORM_REPO_COHESION_AUDIT.md

Rules:
- Follow docs ownership from docs/DOCS_INDEX.md.
- Update owning canonical docs first.
- Do not treat evidence docs as the primary front door.
- If changing docs, state whether each edited doc is:
  - canonical
  - evidence/reference
